race.description: Apg Yearling Sales 3YO C&G Final Mobile Pace (G2)
race.comment: CAPTAIN PERFECT (9) continued his strong form and added to a good record at this distance when he led to win last week's semi-final by 1.2m. Draws on the back row this time but came from there for a terrific second in last month's Victoria Derby. A repeat of that performance would stack up strongly here. ITS CONFIDENTIAL (2) is very consistent having added to a string of top-three finishes when he came from the second line to be beaten 1.5m last week. He too was a Victoria Derby placegetter last month and gets a good draw so looks to offer some value. SAO PAULO SIMBA (8) continues a run of second line draws but has recorded a win and a placing in his last two appearances here and should enjoy a nice trail. FORTY LOVE (6) has been racing well from the back row including an SA Derby win last month. Returns to the front line and won the last time he started from there as did GOLDEN TRIBE (1) who has the speed to take advantage of the ace draw.
